description:
GeranFreqGroup: Table containing GERAN frequency group information for each cell, including timestamps, identifiers, and reservation details.

- dateTime: Timestamp indicating when the data was recorded.
- Area_Name: Name of the area where the cell is located (e.g., NR_Balikpapan).
- CellId: Unique identifier for the cell site.
- Id2: Redundant cell identifier.
- Id3:  Likely an internal identifier (unclear purpose).
- Id4: Likely an internal identifier (unclear purpose).
- vsDataType: Data type identifier.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
- GeranFreqGroup.frequencyGroupId:  Unique identifier for the GERAN frequency group.
- GeranFreqGroup.userLabel: User-defined label for the frequency group (appears unused).
- GeranFreqGroup.geranFreqGroupId: Redundant GERAN frequency group identifier.
- GeranFreqGroup.reservedBy:  Detailed information on the entity that has reserved the frequency group, including subnetwork, managed element, and frequency.
